snippet.title: Quick Draw - Gameboy (20 sec short gameplay video)
snippet.description:
This is a homebrew game, run on Gameboy DMG. 
Original version: John P. Shay - Solar Software Ltd. Commodore 16/Plus4, 1985. 

Gameboy version by László Rajcsányi
Platform: Gameboy DMG
Year: 2023
Publisher: WLS

Online Play or Download link: https://wls.hu/quickdraw-gb/
